			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Do you want to be a leader in the social space, helping the biggest brands and agencies deliver an ROI on social advertising?</p>
<p>
Social is changing the way today&rsquo;s consumers engage with brands. Moontoast is changing the way brands engage with social.</p>
<p>
Moontoast is one of Boston&rsquo;s hottest start-ups, and is looking for an enthusiastic and rock star Solutions Consultant/Strategist to join the business development team. Leveraging a unique technology platform, Moontoast is helping some of the biggest brands and agencies harness the reach and influence of social and drive real results. From our Facebook Preferred Marketing Developer status, to our client relationships with Nike, Ford, Universal Music, and others, Moontoast is changing the social advertising landscape across both desktop and mobile.</p>
<p>
Moontoast is a fun, collaborative start-up environment, and we need people who can wear a number of hats, all while working hard and playing hard (9-5&rsquo;ers need not apply).&nbsp; The Solutions Consultant/Strategist will lead and execute the delivery of Moontoast&rsquo;s Social rich media offerings as well as support business development discussions with clients related to best practices and overall social strategy development. The Solution Consultant/Strategist will work on a variety of exciting social advertising campaigns with an exceptional team of professionals.</p>
<p>
<br />
The Solutions Strategist has overall responsibility for the planning, coordination, communication and control of activities pertaining to Social rich media campaign initiatives, ensuring that project outcomes are in line with our client/partner&rsquo;s business objectives and comply with overall time, cost and quality success criteria. The candidate will work with Moontoast teams on a wide spectrum of activities, including pre-sales activities, project and product requirements, user experience design, technical architecture and solution development.</p>
<p>
<br />
The Solutions Strategist we hire must be passionate about Social Media marketing and Social Advertising and have experience in managing client facing deliverables. This position is a key member of the solutions delivery team, and reports to the Vice President of Business Development.</p>
<p>
<br />
<strong>Here&rsquo;s what you would be doing in our solution strategist role:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Support sales and business development discussions with clients related to Social marketing trends and strategy development.</li>
<li>
Be the Moontoast platform/services expert (SME) on sales calls.</li>
<li>
Lead and manage the goals, scope and delivery of Moontoast social rich media offering by collaborating with Delivery team to ensure seamless launch of the client&rsquo;s social campaign.</li>
<li>
Participate in the presales process by reviewing project proposals and creating Statements of Work. Actively participate in and drive client solutions.</li>
<li>
Develop and maintain successful client relationships.</li>
<li>
Understand client&rsquo;s social program objective, key performance indicators and trends.</li>
<li>
Manage multiple projects and responsibilities simultaneously and consistently with minimal supervision.</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Here&#39;s what you need to have to join our team:</strong></p>
<p>
We are hiring for a number of roles and levels of experience, but we want smart, aggressive, and analytical people above all else who have -</p>
<ul>
<li>
Bachelor&rsquo;s degree</li>
<li>
1 - 4 years successful project management solution consulting experience</li>
<li>
Experience working into agencies and large brands. Agency contacts a must have.</li>
<li>
Excellent verbal and written presentation skills with attention to details.</li>
<li>
Selfstarter with a passion for all things social, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Tumblr, etc.</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
